Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是 Cosplay Vtuber 普洛佩恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這次COS的是地獄鯊魚伯格5中的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,琪拉薇爾唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的直播 我打算在清晨的新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,試著教烏鴉說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 還是一樣胡鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在都凌晨三點了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 總覺得這條街變得有點冷喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 怎麼看就在這附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是烏鴉先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喵 你們在看哪裡喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,手 是手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喵！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噗
